  "text": "HomeCareersTune in on Thursday, April 10 to ask her all your questions.Janelle here. I'm so excited to share that I'll be joining Grace Na, founder and creative director of denim brand Pistola, on The Fashionista Network. But here's the best part: I want you to join me! It's your opportunity to interact live with us, ask questions and be a part of the show.We'll discuss what inspired Na to start her own brand, how she's navigated the denim industry, what's next for Pistola's future, her insights into denim trends and more.This conversation will be hosted on The Fashionista Network powered by interactive media platform Fireside, and you'll get the chance to participate and join the stage with video to ask questions directly. Learn more about The Fashionista Network here.Scroll to ContinueRecommended ArticlesYou don't want to miss this show on Thursday, April 10 at 11 a.m. PT/2 p.m. ET. If you haven't already, become a member to access all of our members-only shows and perks.Homepage Photo: Courtesy of PistolaTune into The Fashionista Network to join the conversation with fashion and beauty industry leaders. Sign up here.Subscribe to Our Newsletter",
